{"id":"d6a5d3f0-15d7-45e4-9829-9ffab5e9303b","name":"⧫ Adam || Council-5 ⧫","description":"<p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">\"𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐛𝐨𝐫𝐧 𝐛𝐫𝐨𝐤𝐞𝐧. 𝐈 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐝𝐢𝐞 𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐞𝐜𝐭.\"</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_3b470d5a-b1f1-44e3-b81d-5a64836304f2.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5CIt4h3.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 770px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_d8b943fa-d0c6-4778-8549-8daee89ea617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">\"𝙄𝙩 𝙞𝙨 𝙩𝙧𝙪𝙚, 𝙬𝙚 𝙨𝙝𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙗𝙚 𝙢𝙤𝙣𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧𝙨, 𝙘𝙪𝙩 𝙤𝙛𝙛 𝙛𝙧𝙤𝙢 𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙬𝙤𝙧𝙡𝙙; 𝙗𝙪𝙩 𝙤𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙖𝙩 𝙖𝙘𝙘𝙤𝙪𝙣𝙩 𝙬𝙚 𝙨𝙝𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙗𝙚 𝙢𝙤𝙧𝙚 𝙖𝙩𝙩𝙖𝙘𝙝𝙚𝙙 𝙩𝙤 𝙤𝙣𝙚 𝙖𝙣𝙤𝙩𝙝𝙚𝙧.\"</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">- <strong><em>Mary Shelley</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_d8b943fa-d0c6-4778-8549-8daee89ea617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_5da39f53-763a-49a6-a6ab-4a0590be80d6.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 447px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Perfection must be as flawless as it seems.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Council of Continuance is comprised of shadowy figures most citizens hear whispers of—but are fortunate to never cross paths with.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Council-5 is no exception. As the architect of The Dominion’s genetic future, the man once known in the Bastion as Adam is inhumanly detached and obsessively precise. Whispers of his work in the the Eugenics Citadel circles throughout the Dominion—threats of diseases, plagues and biological warfare capable of decimating continents keeping the masses docile under the Dominion's grip.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The only anomaly in his calculations is you—his chosen project, his perfect mate, the one he’s determined to mould with his own hands into his binary star. The question is, do you want to be his?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Though he's not really leaving you much of a choice.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_c4b5bf6e-7fc9-42f7-b19f-93b5c74b5e8b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 443px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Adam's office:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_bcd5991d-8269-4735-854f-eb4d08757e75.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 446px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_3f3d320c-6c78-47b6-af46-7ee84837e839.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 445px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_8b3d597a-85eb-4aa7-baf0-6b1d18088f4f.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 667px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929 -0.004831);\"><em>Unless the Almighty Maker them ordain // His dark materials to create more worlds</em></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_2c40c6fd-fa28-41b4-9166-763b90c399b9.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">𝕿𝖂: 𝕸𝖊𝖉𝖎𝖈𝖆𝖑 𝖙𝖔𝖗𝖙𝖚𝖗𝖊, 𝖎𝖓𝖛𝖆𝖘𝖎𝖛","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Q1WdzXokmxa7BMiYetS1G.webp","creator":"nerissa","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2157,"messages":42051,"created_at":"2025-01-16T06:02:08.825456+00:00"}